nodes.text: Alex Fernandez (born July 22, 1967) is an American actor. He voiced Addy Ingrol, Rickard Organa, Shar-Da, Velan-Raz, Velasu Graege, and additional voices in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
Fernandez has also appeared in several television series including Commander in Chief, Without a Trace, Devious Maids, and Killer Women.
